  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t是看新闻的事；<br/>\n<br/>\n每次看到墙内一些app的社会新闻(比如微博，抖音，头条)，都会出现很多道德绑架的言论……<br/>\n<br/>\n比如在一些失独家庭再生育的新闻下，会有一大堆人自我代入，说\"这个父母很自私\"，\"有没有考虑过孩子的感受？\"，\"孩子长大了父母都七八十了\"之类的言论……<br/>\n<br/>\n我感觉非常难以理喻……不知道这种现象是支国独有吗？<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2M1ODkzYjk3NGEzOWQxYzQ0YWI0LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMTMw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7c5893b974a39d1c44ab4.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2130\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7c5893b974a39d1c44ab4.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2130\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7c5893b974a39d1c44ab4.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2130\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzg5Mjk4MTcwOWNiNzM2YmM3NWZlLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMTIz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3892981709cb736bc75fe.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2123\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3892981709cb736bc75fe.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2123\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3892981709cb736bc75fe.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2123\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODNhNmRmOTY4OTM4YWJkNGYyOTQxLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMDQ2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/83a6df968938abd4f2941.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2046\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/83a6df968938abd4f2941.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2046\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/83a6df968938abd4f2941.jpg?width=1080&amp;height=2046\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWNhNzdiOTVmYzg4Yjc2NWRhNTAwLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDgwJmhlaWdodD0yMjE1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/fi